{"tid":1146001,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 低碳飲食: 牛骨雜菜湯","createTime":"2019-05-09T03:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T09:05:53.000Z","uid":30742,"like":61,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c962ab0b0caf8465a36b7419dbb35ac80898a700","tid":1146001,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VN1VBnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVN1VBnY.jpg&h=961ca1a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RVzzvT-pO58  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRVzzvT-pO58%20%20&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=71bea497\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RVzzvT-pO58  </a><br />\n<br />\n呢個真係超級正正子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔落茄膏唔落糖都一樣好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一大煲我足足食左幾餐！<br />\n都仲係覺得好好食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其係個紅菜頭，<br />\n點煲都仲係爽口既！  <br />\n每次飲一大碗就好夠飽了！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/05/beef-bones-vegetable-soup.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F05%2Fbeef-bones-vegetable-soup.html&d=oAUO